<p>I send "top" to the device through serailport,then read the top info <br> After that, I don't known how to stop the "top"!</p>  <pre><code>require 'serialport' port       = 2 args       ={"baud"=&gt;57600, "data_bits"=&gt;8,"stop_bits"=&gt;1,"parity"=&gt;SerialPort::NONE} serial_obj = SerialPort.new(port, args) serial_obj.read_timeout=1000 serial_obj.write("top\n") print serial_obj.read </code></pre>